Q1. midwesst.csv를 불러와 데이터의 특징을 파악하세요. ::: {#f8d696dc .cell execution_count=8} ``` {.python .cell-code} import pandas as pd df = pd.read_csv('midwest.csv') df.shape df.info() ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout} ``` RangeIndex: 437 entries, 0 to 436 Data columns (total 28 columns): # Column Non-Null Count Dtype --- ------ -------------- ----- 0 PID 437 non-null int64 1 county 437 non-null object 2 state 437 non-null object 3 area 437 non-null float64 4 poptotal 437 non-null int64 5 popdensity 437 non-null float64 6 popwhite 437 non-null int64 7 popblack 437 non-null int64 8 popamerindian 437 non-null int64 9 popasian 437 non-null int64 10 popother 437 non-null int64 11 percwhite 437 non-null float64 12 percblack 437 non-null float64 13 percamerindan 437 non-null float64 14 percasian 437 non-null float64 15 percother 437 non-null float64 16 popadults 437 non-null int64 17 perchsd 437 non-null float64 18 percollege 437 non-null float64 19 percprof 437 non-null float64 20 poppovertyknown 437 non-null int64 21 percpovertyknown 437 non-null float64 22 percbelowpoverty 437 non-null float64 23 percchildbelowpovert 437 non-null float64 24 percadultpoverty 437 non-null float64 25 percelderlypoverty 437 non-null float64 26 inmetro 437 non-null int64 27 category 437 non-null object dtypes: float64(15), int64(10), object(3) memory usage: 95.7+ KB ``` ::: ::: Q2. poptotal(전체 인구) 변수를 total로, popasian(아시아 인구) 변수를 asian으로 수정하세요. ::: {#e337e5a7 .cell execution_count=9} ``` {.python .cell-code} import pandas as pd df = pd.read_csv('midwest.csv') df df_new = df.copy() df_new = df_new.rename(columns = { 'poptotal':'total'}) df_new = df_new.rename(columns = { 'popasian':'asian'}) df_new df_new[['total','asian']] ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=9} ```{=html}

``` ::: ::: Q3. total, asian변수를 이용해 '전체 인구 대비 아시아 인구 백분율' 파생변수를 추가하고, 히스토그램을 만들어 분포를 살펴보세요 ::: {#511d06da .cell execution_count=10} ``` {.python .cell-code} import pandas as pd df = pd.read_csv('midwest.csv') df df_new = df.copy() df_new = df_new.rename(columns = { 'poptotal':'total'}) df_new = df_new.rename(columns = { 'popasian':'asian'}) df_new df_new['per'] =(df_new['asian']/df_new['total'])* 100 df_new df_new['per'].plot.hist() ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display} ![](index_files/figure-html/cell-11-output-1.png){width=593 height=411} ::: ::: Q4. 아시아 인구 백분율 전체 평균을 구하고, 평균을 초과하면 'large', 그 외에는 'small'을 부여한 파생변수를 만들어 보세요. ::: {#d6d2f8dc .cell execution_count=11} ``` {.python .cell-code} import pandas as pd import numpy as np df = pd.read_csv('midwest.csv') df df_new = df.copy() df_new = df_new.rename(columns = { 'poptotal':'total'}) df_new = df_new.rename(columns = { 'popasian':'asian'}) df_new df_new['per'] =(df_new['asian']/df_new['total'])*100 df_new df_new['per'].mean() df_new['size'] = np.where(df_new['per'] > 0.4872, 'large', 'small' ) df_new['size'] ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=11} ``` 0 small 1 small 2 small 3 small 4 small ... 432 large 433 small 434 small 435 large 436 large Name: size, Length: 437, dtype: object ``` ::: ::: Q5. 'large'와 'small'에 해당하는 지역이 얼마나 많은지 빈도표와 빈도 막대 그래프를 만들어 확인해보세요. ::: {#403d1ece .cell execution_count=12} ``` {.python .cell-code} import pandas as pd import numpy as np df = pd.read_csv('midwest.csv') df df_new = df.copy() df_new = df_new.rename(columns = { 'poptotal':'total'}) df_new = df_new.rename(columns = { 'popasian':'asian'}) df_new df_new['per'] =(df_new['asian']/df_new['total'])*100 df_new df_new['per'].mean() df_new['size'] = np.where(df_new['per'] > 0.4872, 'large', 'small' ) df_new['size'] count_test = df_new['size'].value_counts() count_test.plot.bar(rot = 0) ``` ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display} ![](index_files/figure-html/cell-13-output-1.png){width=575 height=429} ::: :::
